Title: Relates to the registration of surplus military vehicles
Summary: Requires the registration of surplus military vehicles previously owned by the United States department of defense or any federal agency, sold or transferred through an authorized federal surplus property program.
LawCode: Add ยง401-c, V & T L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the vehicle and traffic law, in relation to the registration and titling of surplus military vehicles purchased from the federal government
